 *   Half-edges, "down" face loop 31: 23 (A->C)  24 (C->B)  25 (B->A)
 *   Twins: 20<->25, 21<->24, 22<->23
 *   Face 40 ("up"):   surface normal +z; loop A->B->C is CCW seen from +z.
 *   Face 41 ("down"): surface normal -z (y negated so z = x cross y);
